Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on March 27, 2026, the following bill was signed into law:
S.B. NO. 3123, S.D. 1 RELATING TO PRIVATE SUPPORT OF
EDUCATION.
